com.serena.dmclient.objects
Interface RequestProvider

All Superinterfaces:
DimensionsObject
public interface RequestProvider
extends DimensionsObject

Represents an IDM (issue and defect management) request provider instance. A request provider provides IDM request functionality to Dimensions CM or Dimensions Express.

  • In Dimensions CM, the IDM request provider can be based on Dimensions CM requests, SBM-item requests, or be the null provider ('NONE').
  • In Dimensions Express, the IDM request provider can be based on SBM-item requests, or be the null provider ('NONE').
